Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ford on Portuguese revolution
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8qky
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Aug 1975
Ford uses American Legion speech to warn Soviets on meddling in Portuguese revolution. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less